description: Just plug-and-play for keyboards, mice, modems, printers, and other USB peripherals. This cable provides a transfer rate up to 480 Mbps depending upon the peripheral's USB version, and easily attaches to any USB device. Foil and braid shielding reduces EMI/RFI interference and twisted pair construction helps reduce crosstalk thus ensuring high-speed, error-free data transfer.
title: C2G / Cables to Go 13171 USB 2.0 A Male to B Male Cable, White (3.2 Feet/1 Meter)
